OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FThe estimated cost of bringing pothole-
OL,8,Fplagued local roads in England and
OL,9,FWales up to scratch has risen to a
OL,10,Frecord #18.6 billion, according to a
OL,11,Fnew report, which branded the
OL,12,Fsituation "a national disgrace".
OL,14,FResearch by the Asphalt Industry
OL,15,FAlliance (AIA) found only 51% of the
OL,16,Flocal road network is reported to be
OL,17,Fin good condition.
OL,19,FIt claimed this shows extra investment
OL,20,Fto tackle potholes has failed to
OL,21,Fdeliver "noticeable improvements".
OL,26,@tD@KOUtD@_O]}D@IOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
