OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773767470
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FRoads are only being resurfaced, on
OL,8,Faverage, once every 97 years.
OL,10,FA total of 1.9 million potholes were
OL,11,Ffilled over the last year.
OL,13,FDavid Giles, who chairs the AIA, said
OL,14,Fnoticeable improvements "lie a long
OL,15,Fway of".
OL,17,FHe said: "I think all road users would
OL,18,Fagree that the condition of our local
OL,19,Froads has become a national disgrace."
OL,26,@vD@YOUwD@GO]yD@JOU{D@fO]
