OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FTotal local road maintenance funding
OL,8,Ffor England provided by the Government
OL,9,Fin the 2025/26 financial year was
OL,10,Fnearly #1.6 billion, representing a
OL,11,F#500 million uplift compared with the
OL,12,Fprevious 12 months.
OL,14,FA total of #7.3 billion has been
OL,15,Fannounced for the four years up to the
OL,16,F2029/30 financial year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
