OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773767470
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FMr Giles said: "While local authority
OL,8,Fhighway engineers told us they are
OL,9,Fcautiously optimistic that the
OL,10,Fincreased funding will help them stem
OL,11,Ffurther decline, it is not the silver
OL,12,Fbullet that will clear the backlog of
OL,13,Frepairs any time soon.
OL,15,F"It will be some time before the
OL,16,Fimpact of increased funding levels, if
OL,17,Ffully delivered, will be noticed by
OL,18,Fthe public."
OL,26,@oD@POUwD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
