OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773767470
OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FHe added that "the dial could be moved
OL,8,Fquicker" if the Government's
OL,9,Fcommitment to additional funding was
OL,10,Ffront-loaded rather than "ramping up
OL,11,Fin the years to 2030".
OL,13,FThe AIA's annual Alarm (annual local
OL,14,Fauthority road maintenance) report is
OL,15,Fbased on a survey of local authorities.
OL,17,FIt found bringing local roads up to
OL,18,Fideal conditions would cost #18.6
OL,19,Fbillion and take 12 years to complete.
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@HO]rD@ZOUsD@UO]
