OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FHighway maintenance budgets for the
OL,8,F2025/26 financial year are reported to
OL,9,Fhave increased by 17% compared with
OL,10,Fthe previous 12 months, to an average
OL,11,Fof #30.5 million per authority.
OL,13,FMore than half of that (54%) is being
OL,14,Fspent on the surface and structure of
OL,15,Froads.
OL,17,FPotholes are often formed when
OL,18,Frainfall enters cracks in the road and
OL,19,F` when the temperature drops below 0C
OL,20,F` freezes and expands, creating bigger
OL,21,Fcracks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
