OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FAA president Edmund King warned that
OL,8,F"much more needs to be done to
OL,9,Feradicate this plague of potholes".
OL,11,FHe added: "We have been seeing with
OL,12,Four own eyes, and feeling with our
OL,13,Fwheels, how record wet weather linked
OL,14,Fto substandard roads has led to many
OL,15,Flocal roads becoming patchwork
OL,16,Fobstacle courses."
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@bO]sD@KOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
