OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FTom Hunt, who chairs the Local
OL,8,FGovernment Association's inclusive
OL,9,Fgrowth committee, said the increase in
OL,10,Ffunding for fixing roads is "positive"
OL,11,Fbut "more action is needed for
OL,12,Fcouncils to bring roads up to scratch".
OL,14,FColin Brown, director of campaigns and
OL,15,Fpolitical engagement at lobbying
OL,16,Forganisation Motorcycle Action Group,
OL,17,Fcited Government figures showing road
OL,18,Fsurface conditions contribute to twice
OL,19,Fthe proportion of killed or seriously
OL,20,Finjured motorcyclists compared with
OL,21,Fcar occupants and cyclists.
OL,26,@rD@]OUrD@fO]sD@EOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
