OL,3,CCost of fixing all potholes on
OL,4,C'national disgrace' roads estimated at
OL,5,C#18.6bn
OL,7,FHe said: "Riders aren't complaining
OL,8,Fabout cracked roads because of the
OL,9,Fdamage to their tyres ` it's the added
OL,10,Frisk of dying on them."
OL,12,FA Department for Transport
OL,13,Fspokesperson said the report "rightly
OL,14,Fhighlights the need to improve our
OL,15,Froads" and the Government has raised
OL,16,Fthe funding level to help councils
OL,17,F"fix the pothole plague".
OL,26,@oD@JOUrD@WO]uD@^OUwD@FO]yD@AOUyD@XO]
