OL,7,FHe added: "We're already seeing
OL,8,Fprogress, with 15% more
OL,9,Fpotholeprevention works carried out
OL,10,Fin 2025 compared to 2024 and reversing
OL,11,Fa nearly decade-long decline in road
OL,12,Frepair works."
